    <div class="documentTop">
      <h1>Press centre</h1>
      
      <p>Welcome to the Ministry of Finance's Press centre.&nbsp;On these pages&nbsp;you will find&nbsp;information regarding&nbsp;press inquiries, press releases, and&nbsp;other useful&nbsp;information.</p>
<h2>Press inquiries</h2>
<h4></h4>
<p>In order to provide the press with best possible service, the Information Unit of the Ministry has established a press telephone: +47 22 24 44 11 (between 8.00 am - 3.00 pm).<br /></p>
<p><strong>____________________</strong></p>
<p>The Information Unit distributes press releases electronically. If you want to subscribe to English text press releases from the Ministry of Finance, send your name and e-mail adress to <img id='Eoi_1' class='obfimg' src='/images/emailimages/77b59f568075af9d3c059bfab6b11b9a.png' alt='' /><script type="text/javascript"><!--
